Smashing store
to manage, this.

122
00:06:03,030 --> 00:06:04,231
I think
I've got it, sir.

123
00:06:04,264 --> 00:06:06,099
I think I've got it--
it's rag week.

124
00:06:06,133 --> 00:06:07,534
Rag week?

125
00:06:07,568 --> 00:06:09,036
Yes, you know,
for charity, sir.

126
00:06:09,069 --> 00:06:11,305
Oh, I see, some local
college or university?

127
00:06:11,338 --> 00:06:13,907
No, no, it's
the store's rag week.

128
00:06:13,941 --> 00:06:15,075
The store's rag week?

129
