150
00:06:53,547 --> 00:06:54,915
Inflation, I'm afraid.

151
00:06:54,948 --> 00:06:57,551
Well, I should think one
about 11/2p, please.

152
00:06:57,584 --> 00:06:59,119
Ah, yes, well, you should get

