I've dropped it.

186
00:08:00,480 --> 00:08:02,349
Never mind, here's
another one.

187
00:08:02,382 --> 00:08:04,418
Is there anything
else I'll need?

188
00:08:04,451 --> 00:08:06,620
Yes, sir, you'll need
an ant house.

189
00:08:06,653 --> 00:08:11,525
This is the model
we recommend, sir.

190
00:08:12,059 --> 00:08:13,493
Won't it get out
of there?

191
00:08:13,527 --> 00:08:15,329
Yes.

192
00:08:15,362 --> 00:08:19,566
