him entertained.

196
00:08:25,539 --> 00:08:27,741
There's an ant wheel,
and a little ant swing

197
00:08:27,774 --> 00:08:30,210
And here's a very nice one
here, a little ladder.

198
00:08:30,244 --> 00:08:32,145
He can run up there
and ring the bell.

199
00:08:32,179 --> 00:08:33,580
That's a trick
he can learn.

200
00:08:33,614 --> 00:08:35,082
Will he live
long enough?

201
