you'll need the book.

204
00:08:43,857 --> 00:08:45,192
The book?

205
00:08:45,225 --> 00:08:48,228
Yes, yes,
the book on ants.

206
00:08:48,262 --> 00:08:49,696
I see.

207
00:08:49,730 --> 00:08:54,868
So, sir, that is, if I may
say so, funt184 11/2p, sir.

208
00:08:54,902 --> 00:08:56,904
