say about an ant--

218
00:09:14,588 --> 00:09:15,689
A friend for life, eh?

219
00:09:15,722 --> 00:09:17,724
Well, a friend for
its life, anyway.

220
00:09:17,758 --> 00:09:20,527
Now, then, here we are.

221
00:09:20,561 --> 00:09:22,596
His name is marcus.

222
