"I'm jealous."

236
00:09:44,117 --> 00:09:45,118
What?

237
00:09:45,152 --> 00:09:46,620
I'm jealous
of your ant.

238
00:09:46,653 --> 00:09:48,388
Good-bye.

239
00:09:48,422 --> 00:09:49,556
Bye-bye!

240
00:09:49,590 --> 00:09:51,258
