00:11:07,434 --> 00:11:10,804
That's what you said
about the sperm whale.

265
00:11:10,838 --> 00:11:13,407
Now your papa's having
to use it as a garage.

266
00:11:13,440 --> 00:11:15,242
Well, you didn't
feed it properly.

267
00:11:15,275 --> 00:11:16,777
Where are we going to get

268
00:11:16,810 --> 00:11:19,146
44 tons of plankton
from every morning?

269
00:11:19,179 --> 00:11:21,281
Your papa was dead vexed
about that.

270
00:11:21,315 --> 00:11:23,417
They thought he was mad
in the deli.

271
00:11:23,450 --> 00:11:25,352
Well, at least he's
got a free garage.

272
00:11:25,385 --> 00:11:26,753
That's no good to him.

273
00:11:26,787 --> 00:11:29,690
His hillman smells
all fishy.

274
00:11:29,723 --> 00:11:31,758
Oh, blimey, that's the tiger.

275
00:11:31,792 --> 00:11:33,460
He wants his mandies.

276
00:11:33,493 --> 00:11:35,963
Are you giving
that tiger drugs?

277
00:11:35,996 --> 00:11:37,931
'course I'm giving it drugs.

278
00:11:37,965 --> 00:11:38,966
It's illegal.

279
00:11:38,999 --> 00:11:40,634
You try telling that
to the tiger.

280
00:11:40,667 --> 00:11:42,736
Well, I think
it's dangerous.

281
00:11:42,769 --> 00:11:44,505
Listen, before
he started fixing

282
00:11:44,538 --> 00:11:47,774
