438
00:19:23,697 --> 00:19:26,633
I wandered lonely as a cloud...

439
00:19:26,667 --> 00:19:27,634
Oh!

440
00:19:27,668 --> 00:19:29,203
That floats on high

441
00:19:29,236 --> 00:19:30,871
O'er vales and hills

442
00:19:30,904 --> 00:19:33,707
When all at once,
