00:19:47,087 --> 00:19:48,488
Now, mr. bysshe...

446
00:19:48,522 --> 00:19:49,323
Shelley.

447
00:19:49,356 --> 00:19:51,592
Oh!

448
00:19:51,925 --> 00:19:55,229
